channel.title: Compiler Problem
channel.description:
Every time I compile it doesn't compile, what I mean is I click compile and when I try to run a client it will still connect to the old IP even if I changed it and compiled.
Can I use a different compiler?
What is wrong with the compiler?
I fixed my JDK version and everything and it doesn't work.
Compiler code:
[code]@echo off
javac -source 1.5 -target 1.5 -classpath . *.java -g
pause[/code]
Thank You for any help!
